# 📘 Design System Development Guide (for Cursor AI Agent)

## 1. 🎯 Purpose
This guide ensures that any component developed from the **Figma Bendy_BethC design file** uses the **new design system** tokens and follows consistent rules.  

The AI agent (Cursor) must **never hardcode raw values** (hex colors, px spacing, etc.), but instead reference semantic tokens defined in `design-system/css/*.css`.

