## 5. 🚦 Development Workflow

1. Pull Figma component via MCP/REST.  
2. Identify boundVariables.  
3. Use mapping table to convert IDs → semantic CSS tokens.  
4. Apply tokens in component code.  
5. Verify against Figma spec using demo files.
